  "lyrics": "I've seen the dark side, I've seen the light side The dark side hits you like it magnetizes your mind The lights I bring you, bring you to see all that creeps into the night It could be you, it could be me, it could be me It could be anybody, undercover ranger I've seen it, I've seen the dark side, I've seen the light side Hey, I know that things got worse, I know that things got better I just don't know which one you are, are you a clever disguise to bring me back to life, disguise to bring me back to hell Or are you just a one way ticket to hell and then it bounces back to me, complete No you just don't wanna walk with you left feet, you gotta switch it up and have it come back That's why I understand why you had to hit me like that, but there's things I wonder, things I know Am I the one to watch it all go, am I going crazy, is it you, shit, is it me, baby When the retiree comes along, pulling you in and spitting you out, don't pause I have seen the dark side, I have seen the light side It could be you, it could be me, it could be me Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah Undercover ranger, undercover ranger Undercover ranger, yeah, yeah It could be you, it could be me, it could be me Undercover ranger, yeah I have seen the dark side, I have seen the light side The dark side bring you into the light The light side bring you into the dark It could be you, it could be me Undercover",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 26.100000381469727,
      "text": "I've seen the dark side, I've seen the light side",
      "start": 20.65999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 34.29999923706055,
      "text": "The dark side hits you like it magnetizes your mind",
      "start": 27.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 45.18000030517578,
      "text": "The lights I bring you, bring you to see all that creeps into the night",
      "start": 35.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 51.86000061035156,
      "text": "It could be you, it could be me, it could be me",
      "start": 46.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 61.540000915527344,
      "text": "It could be anybody, undercover ranger",
      "start": 53.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 75.54000091552734,
      "text": "I've seen it, I've seen the dark side, I've seen the light side",
      "start": 61.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 80.9800033569336,
      "text": "Hey, I know that things got worse, I know that things got better",
      "start": 77.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 87.9000015258789,
      "text": "I just don't know which one you are, are you a clever disguise to bring me back to life, disguise to bring me back to hell",
      "start": 80.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 93.80000305175781,
      "text": "Or are you just a one way ticket to hell and then it bounces back to me, complete",
      "start": 87.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 100.26000213623047,
      "text": "No you just don't wanna walk with you left feet, you gotta switch it up and have it come back",
      "start": 93.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 107.13999938964844,
      "text": "That's why I understand why you had to hit me like that, but there's things I wonder, things I know",
      "start": 100.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 116.95999908447266,
      "text": "Am I the one to watch it all go, am I going crazy, is it you, shit, is it me, baby",
      "start": 107.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 131.8000030517578,
      "text": "When the retiree comes along, pulling you in and spitting you out, don't pause",
      "start": 116.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 138.82000732421875,
      "text": "I have seen the dark side, I have seen the light side",
      "start": 132.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 144.82000732421875,
      "text": "It could be you, it could be me, it could be me",
      "start": 138.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 149.82000732421875,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah",
      "start": 146.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 158.36000061035156,
      "text": "Undercover ranger, undercover ranger",
      "start": 155.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 164.89999389648438,
      "text": "Undercover ranger, yeah, yeah",
      "start": 159.86000061035156
    },
    {
